Package blf.grammar

Interface BcqlListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseBlockchainListener, BaseGenerator, BcqlBaseListener, EmitAnalyzer, EthereumListener, ExpressionStatementAnalyzer, FilterDefinitionAnalyzer, FilterNestingAnalyzer, HyperledgerListener, HyperledgerSmartContractAnalyzer, ItemGenerator, RootListener, SemanticAnalysis, SemanticAnalyzer, TemplateListener, VariableExistenceListener
public interface BcqlListener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by BcqlParser.
